title: SetSessionConfigAspectSendObj91RespQual7 (Method)
text:
METHOD SetSessionConfigAspectSendObj91RespQual7 :
Error
Set optional outstation session configuration aspect - send obj 91 response qualifier 7.

rows.Name: sendObj91RespQual7
rows.Comment:
Parsing Table says send qualifier 5b for activate config response.
For backward compatibility with old implementations send qualifier 7 instead.
